    <item>
      <title>Bessent说，特朗普在任期内没有XI的信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/bessent-says-trump-confident-no-xi-move-on-taiwan-in-his-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统相信，中国总统习近平在白宫时不会对台湾采取任何行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/bessent-says-trump-confident-no-xi-move-on-taiwan-in-his-term</guid>
